{"tid":807840,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥記錄","createTime":"2018-09-06T00:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T10:49:06.000Z","uid":93046,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c11c11d6a48adf6f0acb83ab7c3cd1d85b16110d","tid":807840,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T00:45:08.000Z","msg":"因為之前過咗幾年嘅不節制/不運動生活<br />\n喺幾年間肥咗好多<br />\n身體嘅負擔都重咗<br />\n所以想飲食清淡啲<br />\nDay1<br />\n早餐：番茄雞米粉<br />\n午餐：豆腐肉餅少飯<br />\nHIIT:15分鐘<br />\n健身單車10分鐘<br />\n晚餐：油麥菜，鯇魚湯<br />\n健身單車30分鐘<br />\n身高：165<br />\n體重：70公斤"},{"pid":"2ac0e867855b3be85a0712ea881a9a654e872c27","tid":807840,"uid":28236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"巴定絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8ca0343e16298b19af8ec6f985847d64e619196b","tid":807840,"uid":202983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:15:24.000Z","msg":"留名跟進 樓主成功我就試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18019748e43823311e558e579136fbe40b6d373e","tid":807840,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"諗住入嚟睇圖"},{"pid":"de9ab75d494b5e515dc466463353896b809a4968","tid":807840,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n早餐：蝦仁番茄米粉<br />\n午餐：薯仔排骨，水蛋少飯<br />\n運動後補"},{"pid":"bd5a12b3947e3db9589d80dc2d723571fd0647c9","tid":807840,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"Day2<br />\nHiit-10分鐘<br />\n晚餐：薑蔥炒蟹兩件<br />\n紫菜蛋花湯<br />\n秋葵<br />\n健身單車45分鐘"},{"pid":"f815f7afac54ae24d1a554d226844796d54b1ea5","tid":807840,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"Day3<br />\n早餐：提子，番薯，烚蛋<br />\n午餐：青瓜腸仔（幾片）菜心少飯"},{"pid":"9a55c6fb9919af6f52a7e4e3150db2c06bc5efcb","tid":807840,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":